verbose_text: The results of XTT cell proliferation assays showed that GRO-alpha (100 ng/mL) and IL-8 (25 ng/mL) resulted in the highest proliferation rate in OVCA433 cells on day 4, while GRO-alpha (40 ng/mL) and IL-8 (50 ng/mL) induced the same cell proliferation rate in A2780cp cells.
evidence: IL-8 (50 ng/mL) induced the same cell proliferation
